headline: OOF: More Bad News for Biden
author: Will
sentences: In any case, things just took a turn for the even worse for him, both on the legal front and the electoral situation front.Beginning with the legal front, rock-ribbed conservative Senator Ron Johnson took to Hannity to discuss that and, during the Hannity appearance he said that the Biden “dam is breaking.” In his words“Well, the only problem with the special counsel appointed by Merrick Garland is, I wouldn’t have any faith in them.
Things aren’t going great for Team Biden or for Biden himself; turns out, being a demented leftist isn’t great for you or the country you’re supposedly running.
